Insider Activity


Individual




Richard J. Bressler



Mr. Richard J. Bressler is President & Chief Financial Officer at Clear Channel Outdoor Holdings, Inc., Chairman-Arts Deans Council School at Columbia University and Chief Financial Officer at Clear Channel Holdings, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at iHeartMedia, Inc., Gartner, Inc., Civic Entertainment Group LLC, Clear Channel Worldwide Holdings, Inc., The Nielsen Co., iHeartMedia Capital I LLC, iHeart Communications, Inc. and The New School. Mr. Bressler was previously employed as Non-Executive Director by Nielsen NV, Member-Supervisory Board by The Nielsen Co. BV, a Managing Director by Thomas H. Lee Partners LP, Chief Financial Officer & Senior Executive VP by Viacom, Inc., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Time Warner, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Time Warner Digital Media, a Principal by Time, Inc., Partner by Ernst & Young LLP, Chief Executive Officer by AOL Time Warner Investments, Executive Vice President by AOL Time Warner, Inc., and Chairman by Center for Communication. He also served on the board at Clear Channel Communications, Inc. /Old/, Warner Music Group Corp., Blockbuster, Inc., American Media Operations, Inc., American Media, Inc., Nielsen NV (Old) and WMG Acquisition Corp. He received his undergraduate degree from Adelphi University.



