Running with the Bulls

Bressler represents the world's largest financial institutions. Our relationships span decades, and our success is built on three core principles. We understand your business. We are passionate about what we do. We look for cost-efficient solutions.
Read More











Total Coverage

Insurance law is at the core of who we are at Bressler. We navigate complex coverage disputes and litigation, as well as resolve regulatory and transactional matters for some of the nation's largest insurers, brokers and agents.
Read More











Aggressive Efficient Driven

When the outcome matters, Bressler’s litigation team is the right choice.  Whether through alternative dispute resolution or proven trial tactics, we deliver cost effective solutions to every matter, every day.
Read More











Carefully Designed Growth

Bressler lawyers mean business. We counsel entrepreneurs, start-up, emerging and fast growth businesses, middle market companies and large corporations. We are creative problem solvers who protect our clients' interests while getting the deal done. 
Read More











Worth Protecting

Individualized attention is at the heart of Bressler’s Private Clients practice.  We help our clients build a strong foundation and achieve a bright future. Read More











